high_descs: Turn around, go to the stool, hang a left and go to the garbage can.
Pick up the green apple that is in the garbage can.
Turn around, hang a left, go to the counter left of the coffee maker where the butter knife is.
Put the apple down on the counter.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Cut the apple that is on the counter.
Put the knife down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the apple from the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the microwave that is ahead on the right.
Put the apple inside the microwave, turn it on, remove the cooked apple from the microwave.
Turn to the right, go to the counter that is left of the coffee maker where the knife is.
Put the apple on the upper level counter to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter on the right with the bar stool, and then turn left and continue to stand in front of the trash bin next to the fridge.
Pick up the green apple from inside the trash bin.
Turn right and carry the apple to the counter space just right of the dishwasher.
Place the apple on the counter.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Use the knife to slice the apple on the counter.
Place the knife back down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Move left to stand in front of the microwave above the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice on the plate in the microwave and then remove it once heated.
Turn right and carry the apple slice back to face the counter just to the right of the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice on the elevated counter to the left of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of apple on the counter by the lettuce.

high_descs: Go to the bin
Pick up a green apple from the bin
Go to the counter
Put the apple down
Pick up a knife
Cut the apple
Put the knife down
Pick up an apple slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple
Go to the counter
Place the apple slice on the counter shelf next to the lettuce
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple slice on a shelf
